@0=~"There is someone here who expects me, a man named Tergush'tekhn. Where can I find him?"~
@1=~Barkis shushes you and looks around nervously. "Not too loud, please! And he's no *man*, certainly." He makes sure nobody is listening in, and continues: "He's behind the bar, the door just to the left. But close the door behind you."~
@2=~"Is there... a problem?"~
@3=~"All right. I have some more questions, first."~
@4=~"Thank you. That will be all for now."~
@5=~"Not a problem. But old Tergy is a... private person."~